"Gå til indstillingerne for <strong>Avancerede kortbetalinger</strong>."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1383
msgid "Disable the option <strong>Enable Advanced Credit/Debit Card</strong>."
